  "title": "SITE MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>RESPONSIBILITIES:</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>· Project Coordination and documentation as per ISO requirements</p>\n<p>· Timely supervision of work by workers on site</p>\n<p>· Prepare daily installation progress report to submit to client</p>\n<p>· Prepare inspections forms and attend to all inspections</p>\n<p>· Attend daily site meetings as necessary</p>\n<p>. Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>REQUIREMENTS:</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>· Degree / Diploma in Civil Engineering or equivalent</p>\n<p>· At least 5 - 7 years of experience in in facade projects</p>\n<p>· Effective communication and coordination skills and team work</p>\n<p>· Able to work under pressure and tight deadlines</p>\n<p>· Able to work independently and in a team</p>",
